      "message": "We have been running PS1 of this in prod for a few days now on our server with the largest busiest repo with ~4M refs, it helps reduce pushes by around 3-5s seconds. The improvement is greater when there are waiting pushes since it might be an additional improvement of 3-5s for each other push a push is waiting on. In other words, in the busy case, the normal latency doesn\u0027t go down more than 3-5s, but it goes up less due to contention.",
